page.title: 01GREETE YOUNG FARMERS.
page.content: Y.F.Motto- Good Farmers Good Countrymen Good Citizens. Age range 10-26 years open to Males and Females. Current membership 70, 42 boys, 28 girls. Weekly meetings held in Greete Parish Room. Talks, Demonstrations, Visits, Charity Work and Community work, involved in Church has Rogationide Service, members do reading, prayers etc. afterwards walk round parish boundary-have picnic lunch. Annually take residents from Kyre Park Spastics Centre on Summer Trip, Carol Singing for local Charity. Take part in all Sporting Competitions, Quizzes, Public Speeking, Local Shows, Stock taking, Swimming, All other Farming Competitions. Clay Pigen shooting, car treasure hunt, Harvest festival,Dances.We have 20 comp. cups.
